-- Pietersen Returns to England Cricket Squad for Ashes Opener
-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 2013-07-06T14:34:25Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-07-06/pietersen-returns-to-england-cricket-squad-for-ashes-opener.html
Kevin Pietersen  was named to the 13-man England cricket squad for the opening Test of the Ashes
series against Australia.  Pietersen returns to the England Test squad for the first
time since March after being sidelined by a right knee injury.
Pace bowler Graham Onions was also recalled, while opener Nick
Compton was dropped.  The five-Test Ashes series begins July 10 at  Trent Bridge 
in Nottingham.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  